/*
    This is the customize json file for Karabiner-Element.
    Implement the following keymap modifications:
        1.  fn + w/ s/ a/ d to up/ down/ left/ right
        2.  fn + tab to caps, fn + r to forward delete, fn + e to ctrl + right, fn + q to ctrl + left, fn + j to ~
*/
